270
00:16:53,690 --> 00:16:54,300
Raja,

271
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:55,930
jangan terlalu cemas.

272
00:16:56,190 --> 00:16:58,720
Setelah jatuh ke Danau Es,
Ratu mengalami demam tinggi beberapa hari.

273
00:16:58,720 --> 00:17:00,120
Saat ini, penyakit dingin
di dalam tubuhnya

274
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:01,580
