327
00:19:44,070 --> 00:19:47,400
Wilayah Negara Yanbei turun-temurun
memiliki raja vasal.

328
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:49,740
Keturunan ke-24 dari Kaisar Peiluo.

329
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:52,640
Urutan ke-576 di susunan papan roh

330
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:55,170
Kuil Leluhur Chengguang
di Istana Shengjin.

331
00:19:55,310 --> 00:19:57,880
Panglima Tertinggi
Pasukan Militer Barat Laut Negara Yong,

332
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:59,720
Raja Pelindung Barat Negara Yanbei,

333
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:00,790
Yan Shicheng.

334
00:20:01,550 --> 00:20:04,270
Dipenggal pada tanggal 14
bulan 4 di Negara Yanbei,

335
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:05,870
