340
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:23,340
Penyebutan nama selesai.

341
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:27,240
Silakan Pangeran Pewaris Yan
memeriksa para pelaku kejahatan.

342
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:45,000
Terima titah.

343
00:20:47,680 --> 00:20:48,500
Yan Xun.

344
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:50,080
Cepat terima titahnya.

345
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:53,060
Naiklah ke atas, lihatlah kepala

346
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:55,300
