414
00:25:14,860 --> 00:25:15,310
Aku...

415
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:19,830
Mundur.

416
00:25:28,650 --> 00:25:29,370
Ibu.

417
00:25:50,630 --> 00:25:52,190
Ini adalah suamiku.

418
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:56,120
Raja vasal turun-temurun
wilayah Negara Yanbei,

419
00:25:56,120 --> 00:25:58,050
Raja Negara Yanbei, Yan Shicheng.

420
00:25:58,480 --> 00:26:00,160
Dalam pertempuran di Pelintasan Baima,

421
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:02,750
tiga ratus ribu Pasukan Quanrong
menyerbu masuk.

422
00:26:02,750 --> 00:26:05,480
Shicheng memimpin pasukan
dari Negara Yanbei,

423
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:08,310
